* ''[[Pictures from Italy]]'' (1846)
| valign="top" |
* ''[[The Life of Our Lord|The Life of Our Lord: As Written for His Children]]'' (1849)
* ''[[A Child's History of England]]'' (1853)
* ''[[The Frozen Deep]]'' (play, 1857)
* ''Speeches, Letters and Sayings'' (1870)
|}

