===Other===
{{In Our Time|Dickens|p00547hx|Dickens}}
* {{librivox author|Charles+Dickens}}
* [http://www.dickenslive.com A Charles Dickens Journal] Timeline of Dickens's Life
* [http://withgoodreasonradio.org/2012/06/king-of-clubs/ A one-man show] based on Dickens' musings on the last full day of his life. The monologue uses 90% of the author's own words, and is filled with reflections about the purpose, meaning, and supposed futility of his life on the day of his fatal stroke.

